1. Networking Overview
=======================
Networking Overview
--------------------
In this we will go over the components and theory of how networking functions in Docker.

Docker Networking
------------------
Docker Networking:
	- Open-source pluggable architecture
	- Container Network Model (CNM)
	- libnetwork implements CNM
	- Drivers extend the network topologies

Network Drivers:
	-  bridge
	-  host
	-  overlay
	-  macvlan
	-  none
	-  Network plugins


Container Network Model
-----------------------
Defines three building blocks:
	-  Sandboxes
	-  Endpoints
	-  Networks